.IX Subsection "encode_base58"
.SS decode_base58
.IX Subsection "decode_base58"
Basic base58 encoding / decoding.
.PP
Encoding takes one argument which is byte string.
.PP
Decoding takes base58\-encoded string
.PP
These two functions are just aliases to "encode_b58b" in Crypt::Misc and
"decode_b58b" in Crypt::Misc with some error checking.
.SS encode_base58check
.IX Subsection "encode_base58check"
